      "span_text": "The country W chooses a policy in the policy space I. In this paper, as in Alesina and Spolaore (1997) and [CITATION_1] , we adopt a spatial interpretation of the model by identifying a policy with the physical location of the government, so we do not distinguish between geographical and preference dimensions.",
